					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I guess this happens all the time. A console is designed with current games in mind, but new ideas start to pop and the game makers start tweaking the console, working around it's limitations to implement these new ideas. Then, new platforms are designed, with built-in support for the stuff that needed tweaking earlier. This still happens 'til this day.</div>

